headline: Morgan Stanley sees growth in excess & surplus insurance markets
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley starts coverage on Kinsale Capital Group Inc (NYSE:KNSL), Ryan Specialty Group Holdings Inc (NYSE:RYAN), and Brown&Brown Inc (NYSE:BRO) with "overweight" rating, while noting their strong underwriting discipline and pricing power.
